<h3>🚀 What You Can Do:</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>📋 Manage Reports:</strong> View and respond to reports from your barangay residents</li>
  <li><strong>📊 Update Status:</strong> Change report status (Pending → In Progress → Resolved)</li>
  <li><strong>💬 Add Comments:</strong> Communicate with residents about their reports</li>
  <li><strong>📈 Track Progress:</strong> Monitor all issues in your barangay</li>
</ul>

<h3>🔐 Important Security Steps:</h3>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Change Your Password:</strong> Use a strong, unique password</li>
  <li><strong>Keep Credentials Secure:</strong> Don't share your login details</li>
  <li><strong>Log Out:</strong> Always log out when finished</li>
</ol>

